            "list": [
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "desc": "<p>A persuasive tool, sure to turn the tide of a heated argument in the wielder's favor. Guaranteed to add weight to one's words.<br>Useful in any argument, no matter who the opponent, to convince them to listen to reason.<br>In short, people listen to pearls of wisdom.<br>Ultimately, production was forcibly ended due to mass protests.<br>The needs of the many outweigh the needs of the one.</p>",
